query: SELECT MIN(t.title) AS typical_european_movie FROM company_type AS ct, info_type AS it, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND mi.info in ('Dari','Estonian','Romanian','Slovak') AND (t.title like '%letter%' OR t.title like '%picture%' OR t.title like '%star%' OR t.title like '%crown%' OR t.title like '%thunder%') AND t.production_year > 1995 AND t.production_year < 2007 AND ct.kind in ('miscellaneous companies','special effects companies') AND it.info in ('LD audio noise','pictorial','opening weekend','other literature','studios','biographical movies','color info','sound mix','LD subtitles','spouse','budget','essays','runtimes')
left deep tree min order: ((((ct join mc) join it) join mi) join t)
bushy deep tree min order: ((((ct join mc) join it) join mi) join t)
